ay, for example, it happens one day, then does not happen the next day, then happens the day after that, and so on. You can also say that something happens every third week ,every fourth year, and so on.\nI went home every other week...\nIt has been snowing, roughly every third day, for as long as I've had the flu.", '每隔…（天、周、年）;每…（天、周、年）\n我隔周回一趟家。\n自从我得了流感以来，这段时间一直在下雪，大约每三天一场。']]}]